Class Database

java.lang.Object
Database
public class Database
extends java.lang.Object
Implements the functionality for connecting to mySQL database and executing queries. Contains a variety of functions performing selects and inserts to the usertable, counties, election, candidates, and votes tables. Includes functions to add a new user to table, check a user's password for correctness, get user information, check for uniqueness of username, retrieve votes and election information, check various statuses, and selecting various information for GUI components.
Author:
Kevin Dao, Cole Garton, Timothy Evans
